('LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_FAITH_7_CHAPTER_CONTENT_PARA_3', 'A damaged Religious unit suffers a penalty to the strength of its Spread Religion action, meaning it will convert fewer Followers. If a Religious unit is reduced to 0 health from theological combat, it will die.', 'en_US') ;